# ZKTeco K40 Pro Attendance Middleware

## Project Context
Standalone PHP middleware that receives attendance pushes from **multiple** ZKTeco biometric devices via the ADMS protocol. Deployed on a company server using Dokploy (Docker/Apache). Exposes a REST API (API-key secured) for other internal projects to consume. No ZKTeco software or license required.

