## Architecture

```
ZKTeco Devices (any number, any location)
    ↓  HTTP ADMS push  → /adms?action=...&SN=...
public/index.php  (Front Controller)
    ├── /adms/*     → src/adms/AdmsHandler.php
    ├── /api/*      → ApiKeyAuth → Controllers
    └── /dashboard  → dashboard/index.php
        ↓
MySQL (Dokploy managed)
```

