## Database Schema

### `devices`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INT UNSIGNED PK | |
| serial_number | VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE | ZKTeco SN |
| name | VARCHAR(100) | e.g. "K40 Pro — HR" |
| department | VARCHAR(100) | e.g. "Engineering" |
| location | VARCHAR(255) | e.g. "Floor 3 East" |
| is_active | TINYINT(1) | 0 = disabled |
| last_seen_at | DATETIME | updated on each ADMS hit |
| created_at | DATETIME | |

### `attendance_logs`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | BIGINT UNSIGNED PK | |
| device_id | INT UNSIGNED FK | → devices.id |
| device_sn | VARCHAR(50) | denormalised for fast query |
| user_id | VARCHAR(50) | employee ID from device |
| punch_time | DATETIME | |
| status | TINYINT | 0=check-in, 1=check-out, 4=OT-in, 5=OT-out |
| verify_type | TINYINT | 1=fingerprint, 3=password, etc. |
| work_code | VARCHAR(20) | |
| raw_line | TEXT | original ATTLOG line |
| created_at | DATETIME | |

### `api_keys`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INT UNSIGNED PK | |
| name | VARCHAR(100) | human label |
| project_name | VARCHAR(100) | consuming project |
| api_key_hash | CHAR(64) UNIQUE | SHA-256 of raw key |
| permissions | JSON | `{"attendance":"read","devices":"read"}` |
| is_active | TINYINT(1) | |
| last_used_at | DATETIME | |
| created_at | DATETIME | |

